ider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fchina-economy-markets-crackdown-online-gaming-investors-tencent-microsoft-stocks-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecrackdown%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFeng%20Shixin%20was%20the%20head%20of%20the%20publishing%20unit%20of%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party's%20publicity%20department.%20In%20this%20position%2C%20Feng%20had%20oversight%20of%20China's%20video%20game%20regulator.%20Feng%20was%20fired%20last%20week%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-removes-official-after-video-games-rules-spark-turmoil-sources-2024-01-02%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%20published%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESources%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20told%20Reuters%20that%20Feng's%20departure%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20slate%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nppa.gov.cn%2Fxxfb%2Ftzgs%2F202312%2Ft20231221_823187.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproposed%20video%20game%20restrictions%3C%2Fa%3E%20announced%20on%20December%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20planned%20restrictions%20were%20meant%20to%20discourage%20people%20from%20playing%20video%20games%20by%20limiting%20in-game%20spending%20and%20restricting%20daily%20login%20rewards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%2C%20however%2C%20rattled%20markets%20and%20sparked%20a%20massive%20sell-off%20in%20gaming%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-12-22%2Fchina-to-curb-excessive-online-games-spending-in-new-tightening%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20gaming%20giants%20Tencent%2C%20NetEase%2C%20and%20BiliBili%2C%20a%20video-sharing%20site%20popular%20with%20gamers%2C%20lost%20over%20%2480%20billion%20in%20market%20value%20on%20the%20same%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%2C%20Chinese%20officials%20quickly%20walked%20back%20the%20restrictions.%20The%20regulator%20sa