2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsaira-banu-hosts-aamir-khan-kiran-rao-and-family-see-pics-from-the-get-together-4791213%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Ground%20to%20Transfer%20Adani-Hindenburg%20Probe%2C%20SEBI%20Should%20Complete%20Probe%20in%203%20Months%3A%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F03102249%2FSupreme-court-adani.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20(January%203)%20said%20that%20the%20court%20had%20limited%20jurisdiction%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20Security%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20(SEBI%E2%80%99s)%20regulatory%20domain%2C%20and%20so%20the%20Board%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20conclude%20its%20probe%20into%20the%20allegations%20into%20the%20Adani%20group%20as%20has%20been%20promised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%20said%20that%20there%20is%20no%20ground%20to%20either%20transfer%20the%20probe%20from%20SEBI%20to%20an%20SIT%20or%20to%20order%20SEBI%20to%20revoke%20its%20regulations.%20%E2%80%9CSEBI%20has%20completed%20investigation%20in%2020%20out%20of%2022%20matters.%20Taking%20into%20account%20the%20assurance%20of%20Solicitor%20General%2C%20we%20direct%20the%20SEBI%20to%20complete%20the%20investigation%20in%20the%20other%20two%20cases%20within%203%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3ELivelaw%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Equoted%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20as%20saying%2C%20while%20reading%20out%20the%20conclusions%20of%20the%20court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20mentioned%20the%20investigation%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20Organised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20after%20the%20release%20of%20the%20Hindenburg%20Research%20report%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20rejecting%20reliance%20on%20it%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9CReliance%20on%20newspaper%20reports%20and%20third%20party%20organisations%20to%20question%20the%20statutory%20regulator%20does%20not%20inspire%20confidence.%20They%20can%20be%20treated%20as%20inputs%20but%20not%20conclusive%20evidence%20to%20doubt%20SEBI%20probe.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20rejected%20the%20claim%20made%20by%20petitioners%20that%20there%20was%20a%20conflict%20of%20interest%20in%20members%20of%20the%20court-appointed%20expert%20committee%2C%20calling%20it%20%E2%80%9Cunsubstantiated%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20SEBI%20shall%20take%20into%20consideration%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20committee%20to%20strengthen%20interest%20of%20the%20Indian%20investors%2C%E2%80%9D%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cspan%3EThe%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20the%20SEBI%20to%20look%20into%20if%20there%20is%20any%20infraction%20of%20law%20by%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHindenburg%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20report%20on%20short%20selling%20and%20if%20so%2C%20take%20action%20in%20accordance%20with%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20accused%20the%20petitioners%20of%20relying%20on%20%E2%80%9Cunsubstantiated%E2%80%9D%20reports%20and%20thus%20misusing%20the%20public%20interest%20litigation%20instrument.%20%E2%80%9CPIL%20as%20a%20tool%20was%20invented%20so%20that%20legitimate%20causes%20are%20brought%20to%20this%20court%20by%20ordinary%20citizens.%20However%2C%20plea%20with%20unsubstantiated%20reports%20should%20not%20be%20pursued%20and%20thus%20members%20of%20the%20bar%20must%20be%20conscious%20of%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20comprising%C2%A0Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20and%20Justices%20J.B.%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%20was%20hearing%20a%20batch%20of%20PILs%20seeking%20a%20court-monitored%20probe%20into%20the%20allegations%20against%20the%20Adani%20group%20raised%20by%20US-based%20short-seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%20in%20January%20last%20year.%20The%20bench%20had%20reserved%20judgment%20in%20the%20case%20on%20November%2024%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20background%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindenburg%20Research%20had%20accused%20the%20Adani%20group%20of%20%E2%80%9Cbrazen%20stock%20manipulation%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Caccounting%20fraud%20scheme%E2%80%9D%20in%20January%20last%20year.%20It%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F6250052%2Fadani-hindenburg-fraud%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20company%20is%20%E2%80%9Cpulling%20the%20largest%20con%20in%20corporate%20history%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Adani%20group%20had%20rejected%20all%20these%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20Hindenburg%20Research%20report%2C%20several%20investigations%2C%20including%20by%20the%20OCCRP%20and%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20have%20highlighted%20alleged%20malpractices%20by%20the%20Adani%20group%2C%20particularly%20in%20its%20use%20of%20offshore%20havens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20early%20March%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20constituted%20the%20committee%20headed%20by%20former%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%2C%20Justice%20A.%20M.%20Sapre%2C%20to%20look%20into%20whether%20a%20regulatory%20failure%20had%20led%20to%20investors%20losing%20money%20after%20the%20short%20seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%E2%80%99s%20report%20pointed%20to%20fraud%20and%20manipulation%20by%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20also%20has%20former%20bankers%20K.V.%20Kamath%20and%20O.P.%20Bhatt%2C%20Infosys%20cofounder%20Nandan%20Nilekani%2C%20securities%20lawyer%20Somasekhar%20Sundaresan%20and%20retired%20high%20court%20judge%20J.P.%20Devadhar.%20This%20committee%20was%20formed%20after%20the%20apex%20court%20rejected%20the%20names%20suggested%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover%20as%20members%20of%20the%20committee%2C%20and%20announced%20the%20formation%20of%20its%20won%20expert%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six-member%20panel%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fadani-hindenburg-allegations-sc-appointed-panel-submits-report-in-a-sealed-cover%5C%22%3Ehad%20submitted%20its%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover%20to%20the%20apex%20court%20on%20May%208%2C%202023.%20However%2C%20a%20petitioner%20in%20the%20case%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fadani-hindenburg-supreme-court-conflict-of-interest-panel%5C%22%3Ealleged%20in%20September%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20many%20in%20the%20panel%20have%20conflicts%20of%20interest%20and%20so%20the%20court%20should%20reconstitute%20the%20committee.%20This%20was%20not%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20SEBI%20is%20also%20carrying%20out%20its%20own%20investigation.%20It%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fcompanies%2Fadani-hindenburg-probe-sebi-seeks-15-day-extension-to-complete-investigations%2Farticle67193501.ece%5C%22%3Ewas%20expected%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20submit%20its%20report%20to%20the%20panel%20on%20August%2014%2C%20but%20had%20been%20given%20more%20time%20to%20complete%20its%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESEBI%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenergy.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Frenewable%2Fsebi-submits-status-report-on-adani-hindenburg-probe-says-awaiting-info-from-tax-havens%2F103078360%5C%22%3Esubmitted%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0its%20status%20report%20on%20August%2025.%20But%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20hearing%20on%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20status%20report%20has%20been%20deferred.%20The%20status%20report%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbfsi.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findustry%2Fhindenburg-adani-matter-petitioner-seeks-early-supreme-court-hearing%2F105005543%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2022%20out%20of%2024%20investigations%20are%20final.%20In%20oral%20remarks%2C%20the%20bench%20had%20said%20that%20there%20is%20no%20reason%20to%20doubt%20SEBI%E2%