ief%20had%20been%20questioned%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case%20in%20April%2C%20but%20had%20not%20been%20made%20an%20accused%20by%20the%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20first%20summons%20was%20issued%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20there%20has%20been%20intense%20speculation%20that%20the%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20would%20be%20arrested%20by%20the%20agency%20after%20his%20questioning.%20Several%20leaders%20from%20the%20AAP%20have%20also%20issued%20statements%20along%20similar%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Delhi%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Manish%20Sisodia%20was%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case%20in%20February%2C%20and%20AAP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704259200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F0k799oig_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_29_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-wont-appear-for-questioning-today-in-delhi-liquor-policy-case-aap-4790727%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20won't%20appear%20for%20questioning%20today%20in%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case%2C%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Partry%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-wont-appear-for-questioning-today-in-delhi-liquor-policy-case-aap-4790727%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-wont-appear-for-questioning-today-in-delhi-liquor-policy-case-aap-4790727%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-wont-appear-for-questioning-today-in-delhi-liquor-policy-case-aap-4790727%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani-Hindenburg%20case%20ver