%20found%20near%20Rakesh%20Kamal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20press%20release%20issued%20by%20the%20office%20of%20Norfolk%20District%20Attorney%20Michael%20Morrissey%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20that%20autopsy%20results%20issued%20by%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20Chief%20Medical%20Examiner%20confirm%20that%20Teena%20and%20her%20daughter%20Arianna%20were%20victims%20of%20homicide%20by%20gunshot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERakesh%20died%20from%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgunshot%20wound%20consistent%20with%20being%20self-inflicted%E2%80%9D.%20The%20final%20autopsy%20report%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20completed%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20further%20said%20that%20while%20full%20forensic%20and%20ballistics%20testing%20of%20the%20gun%20has%20not%20been%20finalised%2C%20the%20firearm%20found%20with%20Rakesh%20is%20consistent%20with%20a%20.40%20calibre%20Glock%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20firearm%20was%20not%20registered%20in%20Rakesh's%20name%20and%20%E2%80%9Che%20was%20not%20licensed%20to%20possess%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20release%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMassachusetts%20State%20Police%20have%20contacted%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Alcohol%2C%20Tobacco%2C%20Firearms%2C%20and%20Explosives%20for%20assistance%20in%20determining%20the%20origin%20of%20the%20firearm.%20The%20incident%20remains%20under%20investigation%20by%20Dover%20and%20Massachusetts%20State%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fcops-still-probing-indian-origin-familys-death-in-5-million-us-mansion-4779722%5C%22%3EMorrissey%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20initial%20investigation%20indicated%20the%20incident%20was%20a%20case%20of%20domestic%20violence%20and%20did%20not%20initially%20indicate%20the%20involvement%20of%20outside%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDover%20Police%20received%20a%20911%20call%20requesting%20a%20response%20to%20the%20Kamal%20residence%20at%20approximately%207%3A24%20p.m.%20on%20December%2028%20by%20a%20family%20member%20who%20had%20stopped%20by%20to%20check%20on%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20found%20the%20Kamal%20family%20dead%20when%20it%20arrived%20on%20the%20scene.%20Investigators%20had%20worked%20the%20crime%20scene%20through%20much%20of%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDover%20is%20about%2032%20kilometres%20southwest%20of%20downtown%20Boston%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20Massachusetts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMorrissey%20has%20said%20that%20there%20had%20been%20no%20prior%20police%20reports%20or%20domestic%20incidents%20tied%20to%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-origin-couple-found-dead-at-us-mansion-domestic-violence-suspected-rakesh-kamal-teena-kamal-ariana-4769108%5C%22%3Efamily's%20sprawling%20mansion%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20estimated%20to%20be%20worth%20USD%205.45%20million%2C%20went%20into%20foreclosure%20a%20year%20ago%20and%20was%20sold%20for%20USD%203%20million%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20The%20New%20York%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kamals%20purchased%20the%2019%2C000-square-foot%20estate%2C%20which%20boasts%2011%20bedrooms%20and%2014%20bathrooms%2C%20for%20USD%204%20million%20in%202019%2C%20according%20to%20the%20records%2C%20and%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20slain%20family%20members%20were%20the%20only%20ones%20living%20in%20the%20mansion%20at%20the%20time%2C%20the%20DA%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20area%2C%20one%20of%20the%20richest%20in%20the%20state%2C%20was%20a%20nice%20neighbourhood%20and%20a%20safe%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeena%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20who%20also%20went%20by%20Rick%2C%20had%20previously%20run%20a%20now-defunct%20education%20systems%20company%20called%20EduNova.%20The%20couple%20appeared%20to%20have%20faced%20financial%20problems%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20online%20records%20show.%20Their%20company%20was%20launched%20in%202016%20but%20was%20dissolved%20in%20December%202021%2C%20state%20records%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeena%20was%20listed%20on%20EduNova's%20website%20as%20the%20chief%20operating%20officer%20of%20the%20company%2C%20describing%20her%20as%20an%20alum%20of%20Harvard%20University%20and%20Delhi%20University%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20his%20biography%20on%20the%20EduNova%20website%2C%20Kamal%20was%20an%20alumnus%20of%20Boston%20University%20and%20MIT%20Sloan%20School%20of%20Management%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Stanford%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20working%20at%20EduNova%2C%20he%20held%20many%20executive-level%20positions%20in%20the%20education-consulting%20field%2C%20the%20biography%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEduNova%20marketed%20a%20student%20success%20system%20designed%20to%20improve%20the%20grades%20of%20students%20in%20middle%20school%2C%20high%20school%20and%20college%2C%20The%20Boston%20Globe%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeena%20filed%20for%20Chapter%2013%20bankruptcy%20in%20September%202022%20listing%20between%20USD%201%20million%20and%20USD%2010%20million%20in%20liabilities%2C%20filings%20show.%20The%20case%2C%20however%2C%20was%20dismissed%20two%20months%20later%20due%20to%20insufficient%20documentation.%20She%20was%20listed%20as%20one%20of%20the%20board%20of%20directors%20for%20the%20American%20Red%20Cross%20of%20Massachusetts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20online%20bio%20noted%20her%20more%20than%20three%20decades%20of%20working%20in%20the%20education%20and%20technology%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20couple's%20daughter%20was%20a%20student%20at%20Middlebury%20College%2C%20a%20USD%2064%2C800-a-year%20private%20liberal%20arts%20school%20in%20Vermont%2C%20where%20she%20was%20studying%20neuroscience%2C%20according%20to%20her%20LinkedIn%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMorrissey%20also%20said%20that%20a%20homicide%20had%20not%20been%20reported%20in%20Dover%20since%202020%2C%20and%20he%20has%20never%20worked%20a%20homicide%20case%20from%20that%20neighbourhood%20since%20he%20started%20his%20position%20as%20District%20Attorney%2012%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMorrissey%20had%20said%20that%20it%20was%20very%20rare%20to%20have%20this%20kind%20of%20a%20violent%20situation%20almost%20in%20any%20community%20in%20Norfolk%20County%2C%20particularly%20Dover.%20It's%20a%20small%2C%20well-run%20community%2C%20but%20like%20everybody%20else%2C%20there%20are%20problems%20out%20there%20that%20can%20affect%20no%20matter%20where%20one%20lives%2C%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704258960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F0haft83o_indian-origin-family-_625x300_30_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fdeaths-of-indian-origin-couple-daughter-in-us-ruled-murder-suicide-4790728%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20deaths%20of%20a%20wealthy%20Indian-origin%20couple%20and%20their%20daughter%20in%20the%20US%20state%20of%20Massachusetts%20last%20week%20have%20been%20ruled%20a%20murder-suicide%20by%20medical%20authorities%20after%20autopsy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fdeaths-of-indian-origin-couple-daughter-in-us-ruled-murder-suicide-4790728%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fdeaths-of-indian-origin-couple-daughter-in-us-ruled-murder-suicide-4790728%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fdeaths-of-indian-origin-couple-daughter-in-us-ruled-murder-suicide-4790728%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%20group%20shares%20rally%20up%20to%2012%25%20ahead%20of%20SC%20verdict%20on%20Hindenburg%20case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704258952000%2C%22vi