%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fdunki-crosses-the-rs-200-crore-mark-becoming-the-fourth-shah-rukh-khan-film-to-enter-the-club%2Farticleshow%2F106503241.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20How%20379%20Passengers%20Miraculously%20Escaped%20Japan%20Jet%20Fireball%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Japan%20Airlines%20flight%2C%20connecting%20the%20northern%20city%20of%20Sapporo%20to%20Tokyo's%20Haneda%20airport%2C%20burst%20into%20flames%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20what%20was%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20accidents%20in%20the%20country's%20aviation%20history.%20The%20Airbus%20A350%20collided%20with%20a%20smaller%20Coast%20Guard%20plane%20shortly%20after%20landing%2C%20erupting%20into%20a%20fireball%20that%20claimed%20the%20lives%20of%20five%20Coast%20Guard%20crew%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapanese%20investigators%20are%20scrambling%20to%20understand%20how%20a%20coast%20guard%20plane%20nearly%20collided%20with%20a%20passenger%20jet%20preparing%20to%20land%20at%20Haneda%20Airport.%20The%20airline%20involved%20has%20said%20that%20the%20jet%20had%20received%20landing%20clearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20followed%20the%20collision%20has%20been%20described%20as%20nothing%20short%20of%20miraculous%20-%20all%20379%20passengers%20and%20crew%20members%20managed%20to%20escape%20the%20engulfed%20aircraft%20unharmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20how%20did%20they%20manage%20to%20escape%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20news%20agency%20Reuters%2C%20Satoshi%20Yamake%2C%20a%2059-year-old%20telecoms%20sector%20worker%2C%20was%20on%20board%2C%20returning%20to%20the%20capital%20after%20visiting%20relatives.%20As%20the%20aircraft%20touched%20down%2C%20anticipation%20for%20a%20reunion%20with%20his%20wife%20turned%20to%20terror%20when%20a%20rattling%20and%20a%20bang%20resonated%20through%20the%20cabin%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20sight%20of%20flames%20outside%20his%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20collision%20occurred%20immediately%20after%20landing%20at%205%3A46%20pm%20(0846%20GMT)%2C%20with%20the%20airline%20suggesting%20that%20the%20captain%2C%20despite%20receiving%20permission%20to%20land%2C%20likely%20couldn't%20see%20the%20smaller%20Coast%20Guard%20plane%20below.%20Authorities%20are%20now%20investigating%20the%20unusual%20circumstances%20surrounding%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20the%20evacuation%20and%20rescue%20operations%20were%20nothing%20short%20of%20extraordinary.%20A%20Reuters%20report%20claims%20Genki%20Miyamoto%2C%20the%2039-year-old%20captain%20of%20the%20Coast%20Guard%20plane%2C%20managed%20to%20escape%20the%20wreckage%20and%20radio%20his%20base%2C%20reporting%20the%20explosion%20on%20the%20runway.%20The%20cabin%20of%20the%20passenger%20jet%20quickly%20filled%20with%20smoke.%20Yet%2C%20the%20response%20of%20the%20crew%20and%20the%20efficiency%20of%20the%20evacuation%20procedures%20prevented%20what%20could%20have%20been%20a%20catastrophe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20video%20footage%20shared%20with%20Reuters%2C%20one%20passenger%20can%20be%20heard%20shouting%20for%20help%2C%20while%20a%20child%20screams%20for%20the%20doors%20to%20be%20opened.%20Tsubasa%20Sawada%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20Tokyo%20resident%2C%20recalled%20thinking%20he%20was%20going%20to%20die%20when%20the%20fire%20started.%20However%2C%20he%20highlighted%20that%20despite%20the%20initial%20panic%2C%20the%20crew%20swiftly%20deployed%20evacuation%20chutes%2C%20ensuring%20an%20orderly%20exit%20for%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20thought%20I%20was%20going%20to%20die%2C%26quot%3B%20Sawada%20said%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20Reuters.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20accident%20happened%2C%20I%20was%20laughing%20a%20bit%20at%20first%20when%20I%20could%20see%20some%20sparks%20coming%20out%20(of%20the%20engine)%20but%20when%20the%20fire%20started%2C%20I%20realised%20it%20was%20more%20than%20just%20something.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFootage%20captured%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X%20shows%20the%20aircraft%20coming%20to%20a%20halt%20on%20its%20nose%2C%20with%20a%20ball%20of%20fire%20erupting%20from%20underneath%20and%20thick%20black%20smoke%20billowing%20from%20the%20rear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20the%20aircraft%2C%20a%20massive%20firefighting%20effort%20involving%20115%20units%20worked%20tirelessly%20to%20control%20the%20blaze%20that%20started%20at%20the%20back%20of%20the%20plane%20and%20eventually%20engulfed%20the%20entire%20aircraft.%20Passengers%20were%20seen%20descending%20inflatable%20slides%20from%20a%20burning%20airplane.%20Miraculously%2C%20all%20passengers%20were%20evacuated%20within%20less%20than%2020%20minutes%20of%20the%20plane%20coming%20to%20a%20stop.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704258240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F2r91qvo8_japan-plane-afp-_625x300_03_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-how-379-passengers-miraculously-escaped-japan-jet-fireball-4790869%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Airbus%20A350%20collided%20with%20a%20smaller%20Coast%20Guard%20plane%20shortly%20after%20landing%2C%20erupting%20into%20a%20fireball%20that%20claimed%20the%20lives%20of%20five%20Coast%20Guard%20crew%20members.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-how-379-passengers-miraculously-escaped-japan-jet-fireball-4790869%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-how-379-passengers-miraculously-escaped-japan-jet-fireball-4790869%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-how-379-passengers-miraculously-escaped-japan-jet-fireball-4790869%2Famp%2F1%22%