E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EReports%20say%20that%20the%20ruled%20under%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20(CAA)%20%E2%80%93%20under%20works%20ever%20since%20the%20Act%20was%20passed%20at%20the%20end%20of%202019%20%E2%80%93%20are%20now%20ready%20and%20will%20be%20notified%20before%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20December%2010%2C%202019%20and%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20two%20days%20later%20after%20it%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20upper%20house%20by%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20The%20move%20drew%20heavy%20criticism%20from%20politicians%20and%20citizens%20alike%20for%20ostensibly%20singling%20out%20Muslims%20and%20excluding%20them%20from%20its%20purview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Act%20aims%20to%20provide%20citizenship%20to%20Hindus%2C%20Parsis%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Jains%20and%20Christians%20purportedly%20fleeing%20persecution%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20Muslim-majority%20neighbours%3B%20namely%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notable%20absence%20of%20Muslims%20from%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20legislation%2C%20irrespective%20of%20whether%20or%20not%20they%20are%20being%20persecuted%20in%20their%20countries%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20unconstitutional%20nature%20of%20the%20legislation%20when%20coupled%20with%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%2C%20had%20drawn%20widespread%20protests%20from%20thousands%20of%20citizens%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20protests%20and%20violence%20that%20ensued%2C%20the%20government%20notified%20the%20law%20in%20January%202020.%20Yet%2C%20the%20rules%20have%20remained%20unwritten%20until%20now%2C%20four%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fgovt-ready-with-rules-for-caa-set-to-be-notified-before-lok-sabha-polls-announcement-9092566%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20rules%20are%20now%20ready%20and%20an%20online%20portal%20to%20apply%20for%20citizenship%20under%20the%20CAA%20is%20also%20in%20place.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20going%20to%20issue%20the%20rules%20for%20the%20CAA%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%20Once%20the%20rules%20are%20issued%2C%20the%20law%20can%20be%20implemented%20and%20those%20eligible%20can%20be%20granted%20Indian%20citizenship%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20quoted%20sources%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20things%20are%20in%20place%20and%20yes%2C%20they%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20implemented%20before%20the%20elections.%20The%20applicants%20will%20have%20to%20declare%20the%20year%20when%20they%20entered%20India%20without%20travel%20documents.%20No%20document%20will%20be%20sought%20from%20the%20applicants.%20Requests%20of%20the%20applicants%2C%20who%20had%20applied%20after%202014%2C%20will%20be%20converted%20as%20per%20the%20new%20rules%2C%E2%80%9D%20these%20sources%20continued%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20timing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fcitizenship-cut-off-date-likely-to-be-extended-beyond-dec-31-2014%2Farticleshow%2F106494250.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reports%20that%20the%20deadline%20put%20in%20place%20in%20the%20original%20Act%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20limited%20to%20those%20who%20had%20come%20to%20India%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014%20%E2%80%93%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20extended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leaders%20have%20brought%20up%20the%20CAA%20multiples%20times%20in%20rallies%20and%20promised%20that%20the%20Act%20will%20soon%20be%20functioning.%20Most%20recently%2C%20Shah%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20West%20Bengal%20last%20week%2C%20%E2%80%9CDidi%20(West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee)%20often%20misleads%20our%20refugee%20brothers%20regarding%20the%20CAA.%20Let%20me%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20CAA%20is%20the%20law%20of%20the%20land%20and%20no%20one%20can%20stop%20it.%20Everybody%20is%20going%20to%20get%20citizenship.%20This%20is%20our%20party%E2%80%99s%20commitment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bunch%20of%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20legal%20validity%20of%20the%20CAA%20are%20pending%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20In%20October%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-caa-hearing-mha-affidavit%5C%22%3Esubmitted%20an%20affidavit%20in%20the%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%20defending%20the%20law%20and%20calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbenign%20piece%20of%20legislation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704256899000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F07121932%2FUntitled-design-2021-12-07T121919.360.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frules-under-caa-now-ready-likely-to-be-notified-before-2024-elections-reports%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20became%20a%20law%20in%20December%202019%2C%20but%20has%20been%20non-functional%20for%20the%20last%20four%20years%20as%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20sought%20repeated%20extensions%20to%20frame%20the%20rules%20under%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frules-under-caa-now-ready-likely-to-be-notified-before-2024-elections-reports%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCan't%20Produce%20A%20Kohli%20Every%20Time...%26quot%3B%3A%20India%20Great's%20Big%20Warning%20For%20Gill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELegendary%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20batter%20Krishnamachari%20Srikkanth%20believes%20that%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shubman%20Gill%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108578-shubman-gill-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShubman%20Gill%3C%2Fa%3E%20needs%20to%20start%20scoring%20runs%20consistently%20away%20from%20home%20in%20order%20to%20justify%20the%20fanfare%20around%20him.%20Gill%20has%20been%20exceptional%20for%20India%20in%20white-ball%20cricket%20but%20his%20numbers%20in%20Tests%20outside%20India%20has%20not%20been%20that%20prolific.%20Srikkanth%20pointed%20out%20that%20it%20is%20unfair%20to%20expect%20numbers%20similar%20to%20star%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20added%20that%20Gill%20needs%20to%20work%20towards%20replicating%20such%20numbers%20and%20prove%20himself%20to%20be%20a%20valuable%20asset.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShubman%20Gill%20has%20to%20perform%20well%20across%20the%20world.%20Scoring%20runs%20in%20the%20sub-continent%20alone%20doesn't%20help.%20He%20has%20to%20score%20runs%20overseas.%20Why%20are%20we%20calling%20Virat%20Kohli%20the%20King%3F%20Look%20at%20his%20record%2C%20even%20in%20the%20last%20year%2C%20be%20it%20Test%20matches%2C%20ODI%20or%20T20Is.%20Just%20look%20at%20his%20records.%20I%20have%20nothing%20more%20to%20say.%20Yes%2C%20I%20accept%20you%20can't%20produce%20a%20Virat%20Kohli%20every%20time.%20Everybody%20can't%20be%20producing%20Virat%20Kohli%20(Kohli-like%20numbers).%20But%20you%20have%20to%20try%20and%20get%20to%20at%20least%20a%20bit%20of%20that%20stature%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYxcH2_izYWw%26t%3D55s%5C%22%3EYouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20hype%20around%20Shubman%20Gill%2C%20quite%20a%20few%20are%20saying%20'he%20is%20the%20next%20this%2C%20next%20that'.%20I%20think%20we%20will%20have%20to%20wait%20and%20see.%20I%20wouldn't%20overrate%20him%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20want%20to%20underestimate%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26