m.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffood%2Fviral-video-anand-mahindra-is-impressed-with-this-drink-vendors-talents-4786453%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffood%2Fviral-video-anand-mahindra-is-impressed-with-this-drink-vendors-talents-4786453%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Do%20You%20Want%20To%20Be%20Millionaire'%3A%20Akram%20Fumes%20As%20Shaheen%20Misses%203rd%20Test%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Pakistan%20pace%20greats%20Wasim%20Akram%20and%20Waqar%20Younis%20criticised%20the%20decision%20to%20rest%20fast%20bowler%20Shaheen%20Shah%20Afridi%20in%20the%20third%20and%20final%20Test%20against%20Australia%20at%20the%20Sydney%20Cricket%20Ground%20(SCG)%2C%20with%20Akram%20warning%20players%20to%20decide%20if%20they%20want%20to%20be%20the%20greats%20of%20their%20sport%20or%20a%20millionaire%20by%20playing%20T20%20cricket.%20After%20Pakistan%20lost%20the%20series%202-0%2C%20Shaheen%20has%20been%20rested%20from%20the%20final%20Test%20at%20Sydney%2C%20which%20is%20also%20Australia%20opener%20David%20Warner's%20farewell%20Test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWasim%20claimed%20that%20decision%20%26quot%3Bhad%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20management%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Bsolely%20%5BShaheen's%5D%20decision%26quot%3B.%20He%20warned%20players%20to%20decide%20%26quot%3Bif%20you%20want%20to%20be%20a%20great%20of%20the%20game%20or%20do%20you%20want%20to%20be%20a%20millionaire%26quot%3B%20while%20prioritising%20formats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStraight%20after%20this%20there%20are%20five%20T20s%20in%20New%20Zealand%2C%20and%20Shaheen's%20the%20captain%2C%26quot%3B%20Wasim%20said%20on%20Fox%20Cricket%20as%20quoted%20by%20ESPNCricinfo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20T20%20cricket%2C%20who%20cares%3F%20I%20understand%2C%20it%20is%20there%20for%20entertainment%20and%20it%20is%20there%20for%20financial%20gain%20for%20cricket%20boards%2C%20for%20players%2C%20but%20cricketers%20should%20know%20that%20Test%20cricket%