20its%20versatility%20and%20power%20make%20up%20for%20that%20small%20shortcoming.%20Even%20with%20the%20ton%20of%20attachments%20(the%20nose%20hair%20blade%2C%20three%20other%20blades%2C%20and%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20trimming%20guards)%2C%20it's%20simple%20to%20operate.%20Pro%20tip%3A%20keep%20the%20directions%20handy%20so%20you%20can%20navigate%20the%20various%20tools%20that%20come%20with%20the%20clippers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20quiet%3Cp%3EYou're%20probably%20more%20familiar%20with%20Manscaped%20for%20their%20Lawn%20Mower%204.0%20that%20removes%20hair%20below%20the%20belt%2C%20but%20the%20company%20also%20makes%20the%20Weed%20Whacker%20that's%20for%20nose%20and%20ear%20hair.%20The%20key%20takeaways%20from%20testing%20it%20out%20were%20how%20quiet%20it%20was%20while%20smoothly%20and%20quickly%20removing%20nose%20and%20ear%20hair.%20It's%20fast%20and%20efficient%20and%20completely%20painless.%20It's%20rechargeable%2C%20easy%20to%20clean%2C%20and%20simple%20to%20operate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20offers%20a%20bundle%20called%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.manscaped.com%2Fproducts%2Fthe-performance-package-4%3F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPerformance%20Package%205.0%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20includes%20the%20Weed%20Whacker%20and%20Lawn%20Mower%2C%20along%20with%20a%20couple%20other%20products%2C%20that%20will%20have%20your%20body%20hair%20removal%20needs%20covered%20from%20nose%20to%20nether%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20lightweight%3Cp%3EThe%20ConairMan%20has%20a%20360-degree%20beveled%20blade%20to%20quickly%20and%20evenly%20cut%20through%20even%20very%20abundant%20nose%20and%20ear%20hair.%20It%20provides%2060-minutes%20of%20continual%20use%2C%20which%20should%20provide%20plenty%20of%20clipping%20sessions.%20Besides%20your%20nose%20and%20ears%2C%20you%20can%20use%20the%20ConairMan%20to%20clean%20up%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20face%2C%20from%20