%20easy-to-use%20thanks%20to%20its%20one-button%20control.%20It's%20not%20rechargeable%2C%20but%20according%20to%20the%20company%2C%20one%20AA%20battery%20can%20provide%20enough%20juice%20for%20six%20months%20if%20used%20in%20five-minute%20increments%20(a%20typical%20amount%20of%20time%20needed%20to%20take%20care%20of%20nose%20and%20ear%20hair).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20manual%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20compact%2C%20non-electric%20nose-hair%20clipper%2C%20the%20Royal%20Manual%20Gold%20is%20the%20way%20to%20go.%20With%2012%20dual-edged%20blades%2C%20it%20effortlessly%20cuts%20through%20the%20toughest%20hairs%20painlessly.%20On%20the%20plus%20side%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20charging%20it%20up%20or%20changing%20batteries%2C%20it%20easily%20disassembles%20so%20you%20can%20clean%20it%20with%20little%20effort%2C%20and%20it's%20super%20compact%20for%20travel.%20On%20the%20minus%20end%20of%20the%20scale%2C%20because%20it's%20manual%2C%20it's%20slower%20to%20get%20the%20job%20done%20than%20any%20of%20the%20electric%20models%20in%20this%20roundup%20and%20it%20doesn't%20do%20as%20well%20with%20ear%20hair%20as%20the%20electric%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-nose-hair-trimmers%5C%22%3EInsider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704239693000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F630626ffc2794d00197f4da7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-nose-hair-trimmers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20tested%20the%20best%20nose%20hair%20trimmers%20for%20safe%20unwanted%20hair%20removal%20in%20hard-to-reach%20places%20without%20pain%20and%20easy%20cleanup.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Andrew%20Amelinckx)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-nose-hair-