ladesh%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20Afghanistan%20who%20had%20come%20to%20India%20till%20December%2031%2C%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20massive%20protests%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20after%20the%20CAA%20was%20passed%20by%20Parliament%20in%20December%202019%20and%20received%20the%20presidential%20assent%20subsequently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20going%20to%20issue%20the%20rules%20for%20the%20CAA%20soon.%20Once%20the%20rules%20are%20issued%2C%20the%20law%20can%20be%20implemented%20and%20those%20eligible%20can%20be%20granted%20Indian%20citizenship%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20functionary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelayed%20by%20more%20than%20four%20years%2C%20rules%20for%20the%20CAA%20are%20a%20must%20for%20its%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20the%20rules%20will%20be%20notified%20before%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20that%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20held%20in%20April-May%2C%20the%20functionary%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20much%20before%20that.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20rules%20are%20ready%20and%20the%20online%20portal%20is%20also%20in%20place%20and%20the%20entire%20process%20will%20be%20online.%20The%20applicants%20will%20have%20to%20declare%20the%20year%20when%20they%20entered%20India%20without%20travel%20documents.%20No%20document%20will%20be%20sought%20from%20the%20applicants%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20functionary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2027%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20said%20that%20no%20one%20can%20stop%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20CAA%20as%20it%20is%20the%20law%20of%20the%20land%20and%20accused%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20of%20misleading%20people%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20party%20meeting%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20Shah%20said%20it%20was%20the%20BJP's%20commitment%20to%20implement%20the%20CAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TMC%2C%20led%20by%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20has%20been%20opposing%20the%20CAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20promise%20of%20implementing%20the%20controversial%20CAA%20was%20a%20major%20poll%20plank%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20last%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20saffron%20party's%20leaders%20consider%20it%20a%20plausible%20factor%20that%20led%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20manual%20of%20parliamentary%20procedures%2C%20the%20rules%20for%20any%20legislation%20should%20have%20been%20framed%20within%20six%20months%20of%20presidential%20assent%20or%20seek%20extension%20from%20the%20Committees%20on%20Subordinate%20Legislation%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202020%2C%20the%20home%20ministry%20has%20been%20taking%20extension%20in%20regular%20interval%20from%20the%20parliamentary%20committees%20for%20framing%20the%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20a%20hundred%20people%20lost%20their%20lives%20during%20the%20protests%20or%20police%20action%20after%20Parliament%20passed%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20last%20two%20years%2C%20more%20than%2030%20district%20magistrates%20and%20home%20secretaries%20of%20nine%20states%20have%20been%20given%20powers%20to%20grant%20Indian%20citizenship%20to%20Hindus%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Jains%2C%20Parsis%20and%20Christians%20coming%20from%20Afghanistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Pakistan%20under%20the%20Citizenship%20Act%20of%201955.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20annual%20report%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20for%202021-22%2C%20from%20April%201%2C%202021%20to%20December%2031%2C%202021%2C%20a%20total%20of%201%2C414%20foreigners%20belonging%20to%20these%20non-Muslim%20minority%20communities%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Afghanistan%20were%20given%20Indian%20citizenship%20by%20registration%20or%20naturalization%20under%20the%20Citizenship%20Act%2C%201955.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nine%20states%20where%20Indian%20citizenship%20by%20registration%20or%20naturalization%20is%20given%20under%20the%20Citizenship%20Act%20of%201955%20to%20non-Muslim%20minorities%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Afghanistan%20are%20Gujarat%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20of%20none%20of%20the%20districts%20of%20Assam%20and%20West%20Bengal%2C%20where%20the%20issue%20is%20politically%20very%20sensitive%2C%20have%20been%20given%20the%20powers%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704204600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-12%2F4lq8hscg_caa-protest-bhopal-_625x300_18_December_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act-rules-to-be-notified-before-lok-sabha-polls-4787644%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rules%20for%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20of%202019%20will%20be%20notified%20%26quot%3Bmuch%20before%26quot%3B%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20a%20senior%20government%20functionary%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act-rules-to-be-notified-before-lok-sabha-polls-4787644%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act-rules-to-be-notified-before-lok-sabha-polls-4787644%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act-rules-to-be-notified-before-lok-sabha-polls-4787644%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meitei%20Muslims%20Urge%20Police%20to%20Hasten%20Arrest%20of%20Armed%20Miscreants%20Behind%20New%20Year's%20Day%20Killings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04085450%2FFvO7YL1aEAAlR43.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Four%20Meitei%20Pangals%20(Meitei%20Muslims)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-four-shot-dead-in-fresh-violence-curfew-re-imposed-in-valley-districts%5C%22%3Ewere%20killed%20on%20Monday%3C%2Fa%3E%20(January%201)%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Thoubal%20district.%20The%20deceased%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20Mohammed%20Sirajuddin%2C%20Hussain%2C%20Azad%20Khan%20and%20Daulat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20say%20Pangal%20groups%20are%20under%20pressure%20not%20to%20speak%20any%20further.%20However%2C%20a%20Pangal%20individual%20who%20prefers%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20people%20in%20police%20uniforms%20had%20%E2%80%9Ckilled%20our%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeitei%20Pangals%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Meitei%20Muslims%2C%20are%20a%20subgroup%20of%20the%20Meitei%20people%2C%20the%20majority%20ethnic%20group%20in%20Manipur.%20Meitei%20Pangals%20share%20cultural%20and%20historic%20ties%20with%20other%20Meiteis%20but%20follow%20the%20Islamic%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20at%20around%207%3A30%20pm%20on%20Monday%2C%20when%20around%2020%20to%2030%20individuals%20in%20police%20uniforms%20entered%20a%20Pangal%20house%20in%20the%20Lilong%20Chingjao%20area%20of%20Thoubal%20district%2C%20looting%20cash%20and%20gold%20worth%20Rs%202%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocals%20tried%20to%20intervene%2C%20following%20which%20the%20individuals%20in%20police%20uniforms%20fired%20at%20the%20Pangal%20residents%2C%20leading%20to%20four%20deaths%20and%20over%2014%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20injured%20are%20currently%20being%20treated%20in%20a%20hospital%20in%20Imphal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20a%20group%20of%20Meitei%20Pangals%20met%20in%20Manipur%20and%20passed%20a%20resolution%20urging%20the%20government%20to%20arrest%20all%20culprits%20within%2048%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20also%20requested%20the%20Manipur%20government%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20case%20to%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20anti-terrorism%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20a%20Pangal%20group%20has%20formed%20a%20joint%20action%20committee%20to%20the%20assist%20victims%20of%20the%20January%201%20incident%2C%20with%20Maulana%20Habibullah%20Sheikh%20appointed%20as%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20tragedy%20reported%20involving%20the%20Pangal%20community.%20In%20October%2C%20Sangomsumpham%20Sahir%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Sana%2C%20was%20allegedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatodayne.in%2Fmanipur%2Fstory%2Fmanipur-joint-action-committee-demands-cbi-probe-on-pangal-driver-death-case-699324-2023-10-23%5C%22%3Elynched%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20accusations%20of%20transporting%20goods%20for%20the%20Kuki%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESahir%E2%80%99s%20family%20still%20awaits%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20between%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities%20broke%20out%20in%20Manipur%20in%20May%2C%20Kukis%20cannot%20enter%20the%20Meitei-dominated%20Imphal%20Valley%20and%20the%20Meiteis%20likewise%20cannot%20enter%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Kuki-dominated%20hill%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Meitei%20Pangals%20have%20historically%20acted%20as%20a%20link%20connecting%20both%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20the%20Pangals%20are%20hesitant%20to%20speak%20on%20record%20about%20the%20violence%20affecting%20their%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20police%20issued%20a%20press%20note%20on%20Monday%20discussing%20search%20operations%20in%20the%20Thoubal%20areal%20but%20did%20not%20mention%20the%20death%20of%20the%20four%20Pangals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20curfew%20has%20been%20imposed%20in%20Thoubal%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaulana%20Mahmood%20Asa%E2%80%99d%20Madani%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Jamat%20Ulama-i-Hind%2C%20has%20written%20a%20letter%20to%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20Manipur%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20urging%20decisive%20action%20against%20the%20perpetrators%20of%20this%20heinous%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaulana%20Madani%20stressed%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20paramount%20responsibility%20to%20safeguard%20the%20lives%20and%20property%20of%20all%20citizens%2C%20calling%20for%20a%20high-level%20judicial%20inquiry%20into%20the%20incident%E2%80%99s%20background%2C%20including%20allegations%20of%20attempted%20extortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%2C%20Maulana%20Madani%20also%20appealed%20for%20reasonable%20compensation%20to%20be%20provided%20to%20the%20families%20of%20the%20deceased%20and%20comprehensive%20medical%20assistance%20for%20the%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20instructed%20state%20Jamiat%20leaders%20to%20actively%20participate%20in%20efforts%20to%20establish%20peace%20in%20the%20affected%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20this%20incident%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20communities%20other%20than%20Meiteis%20or%20Kukis%20were%20targeted%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%20of%20last%20year%2C%20Imphal%E2%80%99s%20archbishop%2C%20Dominic%20Lumon%2C%20claimed%20that%20249%20churches%20belonging%20to%20Meitei%20Christians%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fmanipur-archbishop-claims-249-churches-burnt-in-36-hours-says-collapse-of-constitutional-machinery-11687135842800.html%5C%22%3Ewere%20destroyed%20within%2036%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20ethnic%20conflict%20breaking%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20both%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20groups%20have%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20