om%2Findia%2Fchhattisgarh%2Famid-protests-tree-felling-for-mine-extension-in-biodiversity-rich-hasdeo-arand-in-chhattisgarh-begins-2821733%5C%22%3Ehas%20begun%3C%2Fa%3E%20despite%20protests%20from%20the%20Adivasi%20community%20and%20activists.%20The%20question%20whether%20Vishnu%20Deo%20Sai%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20first%20tribal%20chief%20minister%2C%20will%20intervene%20in%20the%20matter%20has%20immediately%20become%20a%20dominant%20concern%2C%20and%20perhaps%2C%20the%20first%20big%20challenge%20for%20the%20newly%20appointed%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20section%20of%20activists%20fighting%20for%20Adivasi%20rights%20in%20the%20state%20believe%20that%20there%20is%20no%20point%20in%20having%20a%20tribal%20chief%20minister%20if%20he%20continues%20to%20overlook%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20priorities%20to%20facilitate%20corporate%20interests%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20known%20for%20its%20rich%20mineral%20wealth%20underneath%20dense%20forests%20that%20has%20been%20home%20to%20Adivasis%20for%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20has%20got%20its%20first%20tribal%20chief%20minister%20and%20the%20Adivasi%20community%20felt%20that%20maybe%20he%20will%20act%20in%20their%20interests.%20But%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20Adivasis%20are%20being%20oppressed%20and%20corporate%20interests%20are%20being%20upheld%20in%20Hasdeo%2C%20it%20has%20become%20clear%20that%20the%20tribal%20chief%20minister%20is%20%5Bwearing%5D%20a%20mere%20mask%2C%20and%20what%20corporates%20will%20decide%2C%20only%20that%20will%20happen%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alok%20Shukla%2C%20convenor%20of%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20Bachao%20Andolan%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2022%2C%20the%20felling%20of%20trees%20in%20the%20biodiversity%20rich%20forest%20started%20despite%20protests%20from%20locals%20and%20activists.%20Hasdeo%20Arand%20is%20one%20of%20the%20last%20unfragmented%20forest%20landscapes%20in%20central%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpread%20across%20over%201%2C500%20kilometres%20through%20central%20India%2C%20the%20area%20is%20home%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20communities%2C%20with%20an%20estimated%20five%20billion%20tonnes%20of%20coal%20buried%20under%20the%20dense%20forests.%20Mining%20has%20become%20a%20huge%20business%20in%20the%20area%2C%20leading%20to%20protests%20by%20the%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20what%20%E2%80%9Ctransitioning%20away%20from%20fossil%20fuels%E2%80%9D%20looks%20like%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20BJP%20government%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20has%20resumed%20the%20task%20of%20clearing%20the%20Hasdeo%20forest%20for%20coal%20mines!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETribal%20communities%20are%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20fight%20to%20save%20the%20forest.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FmsMT9u2KrC%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FmsMT9u2KrC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Avinash%20Chanchal%20(%40avinashchanchl)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Favinashchanchl%2Fstatus%2F1738054081015664657%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2022%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fadani-mine-chhattisgarh-expansion-scroll%5C%22%3Einvestigation%20by%20%3Cem%3EScroll.in%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20has%20been%20excavating%20coal%20from%20the%20PEKB%20mine%20since%202013%20on%20behalf%20of%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20state%20electricity%20generation%20company%2C%20Rajasthan%20Rajya%20Vidyut%20Utpadan%20Nigam%20Limited%2C%20to%20whom%20it%20was%20originally%20allocated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActivists%20alleged%20that%20those%20who%20were%20travelling%20to%20the%20area%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20felling%20of%20trees%20were%20detained%20by%20the%20police%20on%20the%20